Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragged down these steps\Nand taken away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He was called\N"the Man from Red Rose Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that man's name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz. .. Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know if it was his\Nreal name. He used a pseudonym.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A pseudonym?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.49,0:00:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He also wrote picture books.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.60,0:00:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I ... I was reading\Na picture book in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The door opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:00:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was a strange picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was called,\N{\i1}The Nameless Monster.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing here, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reading\Na picture book here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one who opened the door\Nand came back.. .was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was greeting myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.49,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Welcome home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan Suk's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mrs. Suk is in room 409.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Her memory comes and goes.\NI wonder how she is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan? Jan, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. What a beautiful girl.\NAre you one of Jan's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What beautiful flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure that Auntie Olga\Ncan't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie Olga is always\Ntaking my things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just yesterday she\Ntook away my doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's mean, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But she passed away over\Nten years ago, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That's right.\NI'm surprised you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard a lot from Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Where's Jan?\NIs he still at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He already graduated...\Nand became a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Jan's safe.\NThere's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have very kind eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me anything.\NWhatever you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Katrina, in the next room,\Nis very fashionable. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since\NI had this much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I must thank you in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted you to show me\Nwhat Jan entrusted to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrusted to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The cassette tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would have thought that\Nyou would leave it with Suk's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait here while you fetch\Nthe cassette tape and the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forget business.\NThat's our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Doctor Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I said that\Nyou weren't involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say\Nabout that story you told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,about what happened\Nten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But this cassette tape\Nmay be a clue
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,to help us reveal the whole story\Nand prove your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was investigating the story\Nbehind 511 Kinderheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:07:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But my life won't change\Neven if I learn everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to see\NMr. Suk's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in a very\Ngood mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems she enjoyed talking\Nto the person that just visited her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Visited her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?\NA beautiful, long-haired blonde...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You came. I heard that\Nyou would come shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The tape.. .is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Jan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now... He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me to the hospital\Nwhere Jan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Something terrible\Nhappened to Jan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind is very\Nclear right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That person who came earlier\Nreawakened me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But it might just be for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see Jan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you. ..to the hospital\Nwhere Jan Suk is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with talking\Nto the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:09:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan. ..why didn't you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried to keep me from worrying\Nabout you, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were nine,\Nyou fell from a tree, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so worried, but you\Nacted as if nothing was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a terrible sprain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord.. .\NDon't let me forget him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jan is my child. Even if many things\Ndisappear from my memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please Lord.. .\NDon't let me forget about Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go back.\NWhat are you most afraid of?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The monster inside me\Nis getting bigger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Munch-munch, chomp-chomp,\Ngobble-gobble, gulp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Munch-munch, chomp-chomp,\Ngobble-gobble, gulp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.\NI don't want to hear anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your nephew you sent\Nto 511 Kinderheim,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is the same as this child, who\Nhas been drugged and interrogated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know what was\Ndone to your nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's as much as\NI listened to the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hear\Nwhat comes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:11:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The thing I'm afraid of the most...\NThat would be forgetting Anna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyday my memories fade\Nbecause of those strange lessons.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please.. .\NDon't make me forget Anna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anna and I are\Nthe only ones in this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just this memory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I can let you hear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!\NIt's a young man's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he erase\Nthe old recording?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally figured it out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And record something new?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I figured it out by\Nlistening to this tape.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the person who came\Nto meet Suk's mother tape it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Johan's current voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally figured out where\NI should go, Doctor Tenma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He took a vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Inspector?\NHe's so dedicated to the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it's his first long-term leave\Nsince he joined the force!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Lately,\Nhe hasn't been very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He was among the BKA elite,\Nbut he went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know his limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear his wife and daughter ran away\Nfrom him because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So where's the Inspector\Ngoing on vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He said to Prague in the Czech\NRepublic. But does he know how to rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm on vacation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of beer is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Prazdroj, a local beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that the public will accept\Nan investigation report like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know\Nwhere Detective Suk is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And even the former Czechoslovakian\Nsecret police are involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't announce\Nsuch half-assed findings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The media will be all over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But since all those who\Nwere involved have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,With the situation\Nwe are in right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't have the luxury of\Nlaying blame on the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now continue the investigation.\NAnd find out where Suk is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... Chief, there's someone\Nwho wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't meet anyone\Nwithout an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, now is not the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Umm... Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is a surprise,\NInspector Lunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time we've met since\Nthe Interpol meeting two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The lecture you gave at the sectional\Nmeeting was very interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to come so suddenly\Nat such a busy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I never expected you\Nto come here on your vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take a vacation\Nin my current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be busy,\NNew Chief Nepela.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If it's possible, I'd like you\Nto advise me on some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This case is just so chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The connection between\Nthe Prague station and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the former Czechoslovakian\Nsecret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It all happened when we discovered\Nthe body of an inspector
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:16:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,by the name of Zeman with the bodies\Nof several secret police agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Zeman was investigating\Nthe murder of a man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,who was running\Nan unauthorized orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We found out afterwards that Zeman\Nand the orphanage manager
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,were both involved with\Nthe secret police!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the suspect in that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Grimmer, the man who discovered\Nthe manager's murder, was suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But the children at the orphanage\Nsaw someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving the scene of the crime\Nimmediately after it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful blonde woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But the case didn't end there.\NIt spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The former head chief of this station\Nand two veteran detectives
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,were murdered with\Npoisoned candies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They were also involved with the\Nformer Czechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was the suspect\Nin the poisoning case?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A young detective\Nby the name of Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He was Inspector Zeman's\Ndirect subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any\Nconclusive evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But two detectives from a special\Nteam who were watching Suk
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,were found shot dead\Nin Suk's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So where's Detective Suk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,His whereabouts\Nare currently unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The circumstantial evidence\Npoints at Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But he doesn't have\Nenough of a motive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem like\Nhe would commit such a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes. Umm...\NHow do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know of a very similar case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As I would expect of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That hand keeps on moving\Neven when you're on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're accumulating objective data,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And at the lecture, you also said\Nthat you use that data to perform
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a completely subjective\Ninvestigation at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you become\Nthe criminal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were Suk, what would you be\Nthinking and where would you be right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.\NUnfortunately, I'm on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... No, I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Prague?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been going to\Nsecond-hand bookstores.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Second-hand bookstores...\NAre you searching for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked in thirteen stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.83,0:18:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I came to you today\Nto ask if you could translate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,this Czech into German\Nwhen you have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? A picture book?\NI'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you were\Ninterested in such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have a subordinate\Ndo it by tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it for your child.. .\NI mean, your grandchild?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Suk is completely innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As his friend,\NI believe that he's innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The police asked me\Nall sorts of questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but he isn't guilty at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're involved with the police,\Nplease help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll help you\Nas much as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I'm on vacation.\NI can't be of much help to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone else he trusts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He was getting close to a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd just managed\Nto find out her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What was her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Anna Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a really\Nbeautiful blonde woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He was glad that things\Nwere going well with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anna Liebert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ten years ago, the family\Nof a high ranking official{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who defected from\NEast Germany was killed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was one of the twins\Nwho survived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's\Nanything left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My company was the one
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that published Emile Scherbe's\N{\i1}The Nameless Monster,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but that was during\Nthe old regime,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,when the previous company\Npresident was around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Emile Scherbe a pen name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It probably is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He has many other pen names.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Something Bonaparta. ..\Nand Jakov Farobek...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Klaus Poppe, etc...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Klaus Poppe's box\Nis right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm surprised\Nyou found that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just a mountain of\Nold rough sketches, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A pregnant woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And she gave birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.\NYou translated it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chief Nepela.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. There's something\NI've been wondering about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you read me\Nthe last page?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"At last he had\Nfound a name, "{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"but there was no longer\Nanyone around to call him by it."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.44,0:22:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Such a shame because Johan\Nwas such a wonderful name"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a strange\Npicture book.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.11,0:22:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}inspector Lunge, would you\Ncare to have dinner with me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How long is your vacation?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.09,0:22:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel my beer.\NMake it a coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.73,0:22:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like I'm going to\Nbe taking a long vacation.
